---
title: Prawn Wontons, Beef & Umami Veggie Soup with Egg Noodles & Sesame Seeds
description: Plump prawn wontons, beef and silky egg noodles swimming in a fragrant veggie-packed broth—this soul-warming soup is a slurp-worthy delight. Sprinkle over a good pinch of sesame seeds for that perfect crunch, and dig right in!

